<!DOCTYPE html>
<html t:type="Layout" t:pageTitle="Access Denied"
      xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_4.xsd"
      xmlns:p="tapestry:parameter">
  <div id="error">
    <p>
      You are not allowed to access or perform an action on the requested page.
      <br/>
      Please contact your system administrator for further information!
    </p>
    <div class="alert alert-warning" >
        You are not logged on! Go <a href="${loginLink}">back to the application</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</html>